        "description": "Walkthrough: 1) run `Authorization Demo - List Certificates Without Token` to see 401, 2) run `Get Demo Read Token` and inspect `accessTokenScope` plus `accessTokenTenantId`, 3) run `List Certificates` for a 200 and `Authorization Demo - Read Token Cannot Create Certificate` for a 403, 4) run `Get Demo Write Token`, 5) run `Create Certificate` for a 201 and `Authorization Demo - Write Token Cannot List Certificates` for a 403, 6) run `Get Other Read Token` or `Get Other Write Token` to switch the collection to `other-tenant`."
